snippet.title: Best VGM 1554 - Guardian's Crusade - Warp Gate Core
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 151 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HO0rvkOPQww
Best VGM 1748 - http://youtu.be/SuI_RSHfLIk
Best VGM 2107 - https://youtu.be/zS8QlZkN_kM

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation
Guardian's Crusade
Warp Gate Core
Mutsumi Ishimura, Akihi Motoyama, Yasuhiro Nakano, Fumio Tanabe & Luna Umegaki
